{"tid":464313,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"會唔會食埋打邊爐擺盤塊生菜","createTime":"2017-11-10T11:48:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-10T13:57:11.000Z","uid":54556,"like":37,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6b6b6516a04ba50c37757fa20ff0df380fb43e8b","tid":464313,"uid":54556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T11:48:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/10/192930_cfa6e5aa5cc56840043b1650ba993431.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F10%2F192930_cfa6e5aa5cc56840043b1650ba993431.jpg&h=95895682&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n前幾日同女朋友食邊爐放題<br />\n佢屌尻我叫我咪撚放擺菜戈塊生菜落個爐到<br />\n話好撚唔乾淨 我心諗食得唔好浪費 <br />\n照食 跟住佢嬲左我成晚 <br />\n<br />\n今日食大家樂邊爐 我又遇到依個問題 <br />\n係依到問下各位巴打絲打 <br />\n到底食唔係左佢好？<br />\n<br />\n食&mdash;\u0000&mdash;\u0000&mdash;\u0000&mdash;正皮<br />\n唔食&mdash;\u0000&mdash;\u0000&mdash;\u0000負皮"},{"pid":"1cb9c382882009cab6123b49e890b3d66832d687","tid":464313,"uid":27396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T11:49:26.000Z","msg":"你知唔知你錯咩 你冇分比佢食啊！"},{"pid":"7d54aa49b1b6a832ac2da27e27c1c2a343c43865","tid":464313,"uid":54556,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T11:54:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你知唔知你錯咩 你冇分比佢食啊！</blockquote><br />\n成碟放係佢面前，同我爭戈一塊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64c5188207ca93b5b46bd7b17651aa94b8734d4e","tid":464313,"uid":150611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T11:55:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9ec16c0b1accfe0223a9d676b9dc25da4fb71577","tid":464313,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T11:58:41.000Z","msg":"塊生菜先係重點喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"606ffa30ba5e15f383b125cfc0fd80cc359de443","tid":464313,"uid":40965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T12:02:22.000Z","msg":"<bloc